{"tid":1320638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：不滿偏幫警方 荃灣地產舖停播TVB - 李八方","createTime":"2019-07-15T12:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T12:48:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8e6c0bdcca8ecd623b9096f0ea4c88da14099a","tid":1320638,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190715/20729531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F20729531&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjSuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=a53f44f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F20729531&h=d292db25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190715/20729531</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：不滿偏幫警方<br />\n荃灣地產舖停播TVB - 李八方<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190715/large/1563121096_e440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190715%2Flarge%2F1563121096_e440.jpg&h=ff235d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣地產舖因為TVB新聞報道偏頗，所以於電視機貼上「終止播放TVB」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「反送中」遊行示威遍地開花，有網民不滿無綫新聞報道偏頗，建議發起「反紅媒」運動後，有位處「紅區」嘅荃灣地產舖，近日就因為不滿無綫新聞報道示威遊行衝突時，一面倒偏幫警方，喺店外貼上「終止播放CCTVB」告示，以停播無綫表明立場。<br />\n<br />\n八方問過呢間地產舖負責人李先生，佢話開業至今一直用開40幾吋大電視，向舖頭外嘅街坊播放無綫節目同新聞，但最近不滿無綫新聞明顯只偏幫警方，「如果咁樣日日播，啲街坊睇到，咁咪即係我都有份宣揚開去？」所以決定停播。舖頭位處荃灣「紅區」嘅李先生話貼出呢個告示後，附近舖頭都有人問佢部電視係咪壞咗？佢就向對方講明上述原因，表明「以後都唔會播無綫」。咁唔播無綫，佢會播乜呢？畀咗3蚊撐《蘋果》嘅佢話，由於《蘋果》無電視台，裝有線新聞又怕好難cut到，所以現時惟有播Now新聞。<br />\n<br />\n佢強調舖頭貼出呢個告示，並唔係想挑釁任何人，只係想講出每個香港人都有權表態，「希望大家都知道有小店都支持香港人，唔好畀啲藍絲以為個個﹙香港人﹚都唔理」。  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：長輩圖反送中 收工男中伏 (李八方)"},{"pid":"f30694488832dc5b1497fe26b366da1199487cee","tid":1320638,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:31:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻大家<br />\n<br />\n［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1672bbf4ae5f82faff8c5e077fc3c4cfe33851c3","tid":1320638,"uid":181527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"裝有線又怕好難cut<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b0187bcf7196a7c2407d3a1e809fe42a9ace58","tid":1320638,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持警察！支持監警會！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320279\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320279</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f18fc65a27d188f83a7aed71de094923d77ef9","tid":1320638,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}